Ansible in virtualenv

1. Instalare dependente

apt-get install python-dev python-pip build-essential libssl-dev libffi-dev 

2. Instalare virtualenv

pip install virtualenv

3. Creare director pentru noul "proiect"
mkdir ~/ansible_p001

4. Creare virtualenv in directorul creat anterior
cd ~/ansible_p001
virtualenv -p `which python` venv

5. Activare virtualenv "venv"
source venv/bin/activate

6. Install ansible
pip install ansible


python - pip, easy-install
perl - cpan
php - pear
ruby - rvm , gem


